<br />

<br />
If you're thinking of the Weighted Axe (45/150) from Kunark, that one's hard coded so that no pet will use it. (Well, except the 56 necro pet for some bizarre reason, but since it cancels dual wield it actually lowers damage output.)  Most high damage weapons are two-handed, (or nodrop, and pets won't use nodrop weapons) so the higher max damage on hits is offset by the loss of dual wield.  (Unless the pet is low level - in that case, dual wield isn't a consideration and giving the pet a high damage two-hander can considerably increase its damage output.)</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
